dct_title_s: Map of Hawera, Stratford, Eltham & Patea
dct_description_sm: Map shows borough boundary, two classes of roads, house numbers. Includes location map, index, and 4 ancillary maps of downtown areas, scale approximate 1:6,250. "Sourced from LINZ. Crown Copyright reserved."
dct_creator_sm: New Zealand. Department of Lands and Survey
dct_publisher_sm: [Wellington, N.Z.] : Department of Lands and Survey, 1968.
